<div id="review_1483734646" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1483734646" />
    <a title="Nooilforpacifists" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/26071992-nooilforpacifists"><img alt="Nooilforpacifists" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1387729154p2/26071992.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1483734646?book_show_action=true">Dec 28, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nooilforpacifists" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nooilforpacifists" href="/user/show/26071992-nooilforpacifists">Nooilforpacifists</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/26071992-nooilforpacifists?shelf=math-science">math-science</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1483734646" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1223023643751431497">A diary of the first-year post-Doc Internship at a busy New York hospital. It sounds less like training and more like trial by compurgation. The 24-hour Emergency Room shift requirement scared New York into outlawing such mistake-inducing slave labor. But only to the extent of 24-hour On Call rules, or something like that. Still, though almost 50 years old, the book is a must read for prospective med students.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


