        <a title="Keely Lynn MidwinterGraces" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Keely Lynn MidwinterGraces" href="/user/show/4602420-keely-lynn-midwintergraces">Keely Lynn MidwinterGraces</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780922811052" href="/book/show/2129187.Making_of_a_Surgeon">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4602420-keely-lynn-midwintergraces?shelf=2012">2012</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4602420-keely-lynn-midwintergraces?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
